parameters: Umi "Mia! I'm so glad you're safe..."

Umi "It's okay, Mia. Don't worry. Umi and Kru will definitely take care of
it."

Kru "Mia, it's alright! I'll take care of it... I'll definitely save this
village."
Umi "Kru. It's about time to go to the meeting."
Kru "Ah, then see you later, Mia."
Kru: "Umi... I need to talk to you..."
Kru: "Umi... Can you not take part in this battle?"

Kru: "I expect it's going to be a very tough fight... Probably many
villagers will die... I don't want you to come to such a dangerous
place..."
Umi: "That's absurd! Are you saying... I'm in the way?!"
Kru: "No! That's not it! I just want Umi to be safe... I want..."

Umi: "We've been adventuring together all this time! Through caves,
forests, mountains, kingdoms... and even the sea..."

Kru: "Umi... please listen... I will survive this battle... I promise to
come back alive and save our village... If I... if I can make it back
alive... then..."
Kru: "Then... would you become a real family with me?"
Kru: "I want you to marry me..."
Umi: "...I also want to become a family with Kru."
Umi: "I love Kru! I really love you!"
Kru: "I love you too, Umi... so much..."
Umi: "I love you more than meat!"
Kru: "Uh, oh... Should I be happy about that?"
Kru: "Alright... thank you... That's why I will definitely come back..."
Kru: "So... please wait for me no matter what."
Umi: "I understand... You must come back."
Kru: "Ah, Mia! I will definitely come back."
Kru: "Well then... it's about time I go."
Kru: "Don't look so sad! It'll be okay!"
Umi "Mia... I wonder if Kru will return safely..."
Umi "Yeah... I'm so anxious, it feels like my chest is being crushed..."
Umi "Eh? Kru will die if it stays like this?"
Umi "Yeah... with this... with this power..."
